I just learnt myself. You fall over you get

00:02:36.269 --> 00:02:41.440
up, I don't need a tutor to tell me, you know
this is how movement looks in the 20th century.

00:02:41.440 --> 00:02:42.880
I just sit at the bus stop.

00:02:44.160 --> 00:02:46.160
4. Censoriousness.

00:02:48.160 --> 00:02:54.319
So it was the village counciller. There all in the bed and breakfast and that's where
it begins. It's this kind of orgy situation

00:02:54.319 --> 00:02:59.840
and I think first of all it's abuse of power.
But why people need to commit to group sex?

00:02:59.840 --> 00:03:00.800
I find it so weird.

00:03:02.160 --> 00:03:05.280
We can often grow censorious
and disapproving of certain people and behaviours

00:03:05.280 --> 00:03:08.880
to ward off an awareness that a part of us
in fact really likes the condemmed element.

00:03:11.440 --> 00:03:16.720
and kind of creepy and discusting, I just.
I do not want to be in a harness doing that

00:03:16.720 --> 00:03:18.880
