00:04:15.840 --> 00:04:17.840
Feeling offended
takes up all our attention. It muddies the

00:04:17.850 --> 00:04:22.330
waters. When we are defensive, we no longer
pay attention to information that may - at

00:04:22.330 --> 00:04:23.760
