00:04:42.560 --> 00:04:46.320
The problem with lying to ourselves
is that in so doing. We miss out on key opportunities for growth.

00:04:47.840 --> 00:04:53.600
Don't tell me how to do my craft
in front of my friends. I know what I'm doing.

00:04:53.600 --> 00:04:55.040
